OL,3,CWhistleblower says billions wasted on
OL,4,Cunfit PPE during Covid pandemic
OL,6,FUnder pressure to respond quickly to
OL,7,Foffers, a high-priority 'VIP lane' was
OL,8,Festablished by civil servants to deal
OL,9,Fwith offers coming via government
OL,10,Fministers, MPs or senior officials
OL,11,Fthat were thought to be most credible.
OL,13,FThe VIP lane led to the approval of
OL,14,Fcontracts worth billions of pounds.
OL,16,FSome of the companies involved did
OL,17,Fhave some relevant experience, but
OL,18,Fothers had never made PPE or any kind
OL,19,Fof safety equipment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
