OL,3,CWhistleblower says billions wasted on
OL,4,Cunfit PPE during Covid pandemic
OL,6,FMeanwhile, safety equipment suppliers
OL,7,Fwith decades of experience say they
OL,8,Ftried and tried again to contact the
OL,9,Fgovernment to offer their services,
OL,10,Fbut were being ignored.
OL,12,FA civil servant who worked in
OL,13,Fprocurement at the Department of
OL,14,FHealth felt they were buying kits at
OL,15,Fridiculous prices, not negotiating
OL,16,Fenough and not trying to get the best
OL,17,Fdeal.
