OL,3,CWhistleblower says billions wasted on
OL,4,Cunfit PPE during Covid pandemic
OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV's Exposure
OL,7,Fprogramme, he said he was "disgusted
OL,8,Fby the amount of money these companies
OL,9,Fwere making".
OL,11,FGovernment ministers say they were not
OL,12,Finvolved in decisions about contracts,
OL,13,Fand that they were just forwarding
OL,14,Fpromising bids to civil servants and
OL,15,Fthat all PPE offers went through the
OL,16,Fsame checks.
OL,18,FDoctors also reported that some of the
OL,19,Fprotective equipment procured simply
OL,20,Fwasn't fit for purpose.
