OL,6,FOne described face masks with ear
OL,7,Floops which fell off, and gowns that
OL,8,F"fell apart in your hands".
OL,10,FBy the end of the pandemic, the
OL,11,Fgovernment's expenditure on PPE left
OL,12,Fit with enormous stockpiles, ten
OL,13,Fbillion pounds' worth of equipment,
OL,14,Fwhich was never used.
