OL,6,FStoring it was expensive - so much of
OL,7,Fit was simply incinerated.
OL,9,FThe pandemic was a national emergency,
OL,10,Fin which the UK found itself in a
OL,11,Ffierce global competition for the
OL,12,Ftools needed to fight the disease.
OL,14,FMinisters in the Conservative
OL,15,Fgovernment at the time have always
OL,16,Fsaid their priority was to save lives
OL,17,Fand protect the NHS.
